detailResultFields.value:
Ability to communicate in everyday situations; speak and write about past events; familiarity with contemporary Danish culture. Improve your ability to express your own ideas and experiences by exploring social and political topics and traditions present in Denmark today. Cultural topics include: Living Danishly and design, translation, food culture and fastelavn

PREREQUISITES: DANI 100 or equivalent.
Book: Puls 1, Chapters 4-6
